contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|unga}} '''Unga''' may refer to: * [[Tēvita ʻUnga]] (c. 1824 – 1879), Tongan Crown Prince and Prime Minister * [[Harvey Unga]] (born 1988), American football running back * [[Unga, Alaska]], United States * [[Unga (animal)]], the largest land-living arthropod in the world * [[Unga (fish)]], ''Sarotherodon linnellii'' of Cameroon, black talapia * [[Unga (unit)]], a traditional Scottish land measurement * [[Unga Group]], a flour milling company * [[Unga L.T.D.]], Tanzania * [[Unga Station]], a railway station in Japan ==See also== * [[United Nations General Assembly]] * [[Unga Island]] {{disambig}}
